  'Use Gadgets': 'Nobody needs to make a skill roll to use devices and technologies that are in common use in the era and setting of the game. However, making effective use of highly-specialized or technical apparatus is a different question. Use Gadgets is an umbrella skill allowing your Protagonist to successfully use all manner of common technical devices.',
